Show HN: StorageX – An all-in-one localstorage/sessionstorage/cookie manager
text:
Hey everyone, my friend and I created this browser extension for developers as a toolset to manage browser storage(local/session/cookies).

Though this was started with just the share feature where in you can share storage across tabs (personal use case for Rahul in his organisation which inspired StorageX), but it has grown into a multi-featured toolset to manage all browsers storages.

And plan is to add more features going forward and make it a single extension you'll need for any operations on browser storage.

Please give it a look and let us know your thoughts/suggestions!
